{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ida89b0c08-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1133"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1133"},"text":"§ 1133.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Bronze Star: limitation on persons eligible to receive","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The decoration known as the “Bronze Star” may only be awarded to a member of a military force who—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida89b0c09-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1133/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" at the time of the events for which the decoration is to be awarded, was serving in a geographic area in which special pay is authorized under section 310 or paragraph (1) or (3) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t37/s351/a"},"text":"section 351(a) of title 37","children":[],"tail":"; or"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida89d54fa-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1133/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" receives special pay under section 310 or paragraph (1) or (3) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t37/s351/a"},"text":"section 351(a) of title 37","children":[],"tail":" as a result of those events."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"ida89d54fb-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/398/s1/dA"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–398, § 1 [[div. A]","children":[],"tail":", title V, § 541(a)], "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-10-30"},"text":"Oct. 30, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/1654"},"text":"114 Stat. 1654","children":[],"tail":", 1654A–114; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/383/dA/tV/s571/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–383, div. A, title V, § 571(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2011-01-07"},"text":"Jan. 7, 2011","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/4222"},"text":"124 Stat. 4222","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"ida89d54fc-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"ida89d54fd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"ida89d54fe-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2011—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/383"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–383","children":[],"tail":" amended section generally. Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “The decoration known as the ‘Bronze Star’ may only be awarded to a member of the armed forces who is in receipt of special pay under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t37/s310"},"text":"section 310 of title 37","children":[],"tail":" at the time of the events for which the decoration is to be awarded or who receives such pay as a result of those events.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"ida89d54ff-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","